  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个基于OAuth2的安全访问状态机。用户从初始未授权状态开始，通过扫描\"Start\"进入已签到状态，扫描\"End\"则标记为已出席。但这里有个陷阱——如果在Absent状态直接扫\"End\"，要触发Error状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。所以Absent是起点，[Security_OAuth2]作为初始节点通过\"Инициализация\"指向它。我注意到CheckedIn有个自循环——这是做什么用的？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，那个自循环是IntrusionDetection触发的。如果用户在CheckedIn时再次扫描\"Start\"，系统要检测异常行为，所以标注Security_IntrusionDetection。另外Attended状态也有自循环，由ZeroTrust处理，无论扫\"Start\"还是\"End\"都要持续验证信任。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection",
        "Security_ZeroTrust"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主流程画出来：OAuth2初始化到Absent，Absent经\"Start\"扫描到CheckedIn，CheckedIn经\"End\"扫描到Attended。两个自循环也加上了。现在处理Error分支——Absent直接扫\"End\"会进Error，并且需要能重置回Absent？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Error状态要支持\"Сброс / Очистка ошибки\"返回Absent。另外请在Error右边加个注释，说明这是\"Некорректное действие\"，关联Security_Encryption做错误加密记录。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Error",
        "Absent",
        "Security_Encryption"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成。主状态机结构：OAuth2→Absent→CheckedIn→Attended，加上Error分支和重置路径，两个自循环分别标注IntrusionDetection和ZeroTrust，Error旁加了Security_Encryption的注释。需要调整什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Security_OAuth2",
        "Absent",
        "CheckedIn",
        "Attended",
        "Error",
        "Security_IntrusionDetection",
